	 383 |                          const char **argv) {
	     |                          ~~~~~~~~~~~~~^~~~

	* modules/pam_setquota/pam_setquota.c (pam_sm_open_session): Mark
	'flags' parameter as unused.  Remove unused 'ep' and 'ul' variables.
	(pam_sm_close_session): Mark all parameters as unused.

