	To be able to set CFLAGS from make command-line but not to lose the
	warning flags.

	* configure.ac: Put warning flags to WARN_CFLAGS instead of CFLAGS.
	* */Makefile.am: Apply WARN_CFLAGS to AM_CFLAGS.

