	log it using pam_syslog.
	(pam_sm_authenticate, pam_sm_setcred, pam_sm_chauthtok,
	pam_sm_acct_mgmt, pam_sm_open_session, pam_sm_close_session): Pass
	"flags" argument to log_items.

